snippet.title: Net That Haul FPL
snippet.description:
Make sure you Net that FPL Haul with co-hosts @FPLMariner @FPLlens @FPLNima and @Hibbo_FPL

Map out your FPL Journey with the weekly FPL LIVE Compass show for a review of the previous Gameweek, @FPLNima 's Transfer trends, Hibbo's hammer breaking the Template and much more, incl Q&A

Closer to Game Week deadlines the Match Up Show will also be LIVE covering @FPLMariner's Fixture difficulty rating (FDR), @FPLlens weekly match up feature, Guest Features and our famous Captaincy Metric which returned an amazing 79% success rate in 20/21. Also dont miss the fun #catpick ably assisted by Mariner's cat Oliver. Let's Net that Haul together ! 

Join the Net that Haul Mini-league :  fg1xnb

Become a "Hauler" subscribe to NET THAT HAUL now !
